#: backends/bluez/bluez-backend.vala:734
msgid ""
"No BlueZ 5 object manager running, so the BlueZ backend will be inactive. "
"Either your BlueZ installation is too old (only version 5 is supported) or "
"the service can’t be started."
msgstr "ບໍ່ມີໂຕຈັດການ object ຂອງ BlueZ 5 ເຮັດວຽກຢູ່, ດັ່ງນັ້ນ backend ຂອງ BlueZ ຈະບໍ່ເຮັດວຽກ. ອາດເປັນຍ້ອນການຕິດຕັ້ງ BlueZ ຂອງທ່ານເກົ່າເກີນໄປ (ຮອງຮັບສະເພາະເວີຊັນ 5 ເທົ່ານັ້ນ) ຫຼືບໍ່ສາມາດເລີ່ມການບໍລິການໄດ້."

#: backends/bluez/bluez-backend.vala:747
msgid ""
"Error connecting to OBEX transfer daemon over D-Bus. Ensure BlueZ and obexd "
"are installed."
msgstr "ຜິດພາດໃນການເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ຫາ OBEX transfer daemon ຜ່ານ D-Bus. ກະລຸນາກວດສອບໃຫ້ແນ່ໃຈວ່າໄດ້ຕິດຕັ້ງ BlueZ ແລະ obexd ແລ້ວ."

#. Translators: the parameter is an error message.
#: backends/bluez/bluez-persona-store.vala:385
#, c-format
msgid "Error reading the transferred address book file: %s"
msgstr "ຜິດພາດໃນການອ່ານໄຟລ໌ປຶ້ມທີ່ຢູ່ທີ່ຖືກໂອນມາ: %s"

#. Translators: the first parameter is the name of the
#. * failed transfer, and the second is a Bluetooth device
#. * alias.
#. Translators: the first parameter is the name of the failed
#. * transfer, and the second is a Bluetooth device alias.
#: backends/bluez/bluez-persona-store.vala:676
#: backends/bluez/bluez-persona-store.vala:698
#, c-format
msgid ""
"Error during transfer of the address book ‘%s’ from Bluetooth device ‘%s’."
msgstr "ຜິດພາດລະຫວ່າງການໂອນປຶ້ມທີ່ຢູ່ ‘%s’ ຈາກອຸປະກອນ Bluetooth ‘%s’."

#: backends/bluez/bluez-persona-store.vala:792
#, c-format
msgid ""
"Permission to access the address book on Bluetooth device ‘%s’ was denied by "
"the user."
msgstr "ການອະນຸຍາດໃຫ້ເຂົ້າເຖິງປຶ້ມທີ່ຢູ່ເທິງອຸປະກອນ Bluetooth ‘%s’ ຖືກປະຕິເສດໂດຍຜູ້ໃຊ້."

#. Translators: the first parameter is a Bluetooth device
#. * alias, and the second is an error message.
#: backends/bluez/bluez-persona-store.vala:799
#, c-format
msgid "An OBEX address book transfer from device ‘%s’ could not be started: %s"
msgstr "ການໂອນປຶ້ມທີ່ຢູ່ແບບ OBEX ຈາກອຸປະກອນ ‘%s’ ບໍ່ສາມາດເລີ່ມຕົ້ນໄດ້: %s"

#. Translators: the first parameter is a Bluetooth device
#. * alias, and the second is an error message.
#: backends/bluez/bluez-persona-store.vala:839
#, c-format
msgid "The OBEX address book transfer from device ‘%s’ failed: %s"
msgstr "ການໂອນປຶ້ມທີ່ຢູ່ແບບ OBEX ຈາກອຸປະກອນ ‘%s’ ລົ້ມເຫຼວ: %s"

#. Translators: the first parameter is a Bluetooth device
#. * alias, and the second is an error message.
#: backends/bluez/bluez-persona-store.vala:856
#, c-format
msgid ""
"Error during transfer of the address book from Bluetooth device ‘%s’: %s"
msgstr "ຜິດພາດລະຫວ່າງການໂອນປຶ້ມທີ່ຢູ່ຈາກອຸປະກອນ Bluetooth ‘%s’: %s"

#: backends/bluez/bluez-persona-store.vala:1073
#, c-format
msgid "Bluetooth device ‘%s’ disappeared during address book transfer."
msgstr "ອຸປະກອນ Bluetooth ‘%s’ ຫາຍໄປໃນລະຫວ່າງການໂອນປຶ້ມທີ່ຢູ່."

#. The timeout after which we consider a property change to have failed if we
#. * haven't received a property change notification for it.
#. seconds
#. The timeout after which we consider a contact addition to have failed if we
#. * haven't received an object addition signal for it.
#. seconds
#. Translators: This should be translated to the name of the “Starred in
#. * Android” group in Google Contacts for your language. If Google have not
#. * localised the group for your language, or Google Contacts isn't available
#. * in your language, please *do not* translate this string (i.e. just copy
#. * the msgid to the msgstr unchanged).
#: backends/eds/lib/edsf-persona-store.vala:69
msgid "Starred in Android"
msgstr "ຕິດດາວໃນ Android"

#. Translators: the first parameter is an address book
#. * URI and the second is a persona UID.
#: backends/eds/lib/edsf-persona-store.vala:641
#, c-format
msgid "Address book ‘%s’ is offline, so contact ‘%s’ cannot be removed."
msgstr "ປຶ້ມທີ່ຢູ່ ‘%s’ ອອຟໄລນ໌ຢູ່, ດັ່ງນັ້ນຈຶ່ງບໍ່ສາມາດລຶບລາຍຊື່ຜູ່ຕິດຕໍ່ ‘%s’ ໄດ້."

#. Translators: the first parameter is an address book
#. * URI and the second is an error message.
#: backends/eds/lib/edsf-persona-store.vala:647
#, c-format
msgid "Permission denied to remove contact ‘%s’: %s"
msgstr "ການອະນຸຍາດໃຫ້ລຶບລາຍຊື່ຜູ່ຕິດຕໍ່ ‘%s’ ຖືກປະຕິເສດ: %s"

#. Translators: the parameter is an error message.
#: backends/eds/lib/edsf-persona-store.vala:652
#, c-format
msgid "Removing contacts isn’t supported by this persona store: %s"
msgstr "ການລຶບລາຍຊື່ຜູ່ຕິດຕໍ່ບໍ່ຮອງຮັບໂດຍ persona store ນີ້: %s"

#: backends/eds/lib/edsf-persona-store.vala:681
#, c-format
msgid "Can’t remove contact ‘%s’: %s"
msgstr "ບໍ່ສາມາດລຶບລາຍຊື່ຜູ່ຕິດຕໍ່ ‘%s’ ໄດ້: %s"

#. Translators: the parameter is an address book
#. * URI.
#: backends/eds/lib/edsf-persona-store.vala:770
#: backends/eds/lib/edsf-persona-store.vala:963
#, c-format
msgid "Address book ‘%s’ is offline."
msgstr "ປຶ້ມທີ່ຢູ່ ‘%s’ ອອຟໄລນ໌ຢູ່."

#. Translators: the first parameter is an address
#. * book URI and the second is an error message.
#: backends/eds/lib/edsf-persona-store.vala:775
#: backends/eds/lib/edsf-persona-store.vala:968
#, c-format
msgid "Permission denied to open address book ‘%s’: %s"
msgstr "ການອະນຸຍາດໃຫ້ເປີດປຶ້ມທີ່ຢູ່ ‘%s’ ຖືກປະຕິເສດ: %s"

#. Translators: the first parameter is an address book URI
#. * and the second is an error message.
#: backends/eds/lib/edsf-persona-store.vala:808
#, c-format
msgid "Couldn’t open address book ‘%s’: %s"
msgstr "ບໍ່ສາມາດເປີດປຶ້ມທີ່ຢູ່ ‘%s’ ໄດ້: %s"

#. Translators: the parameteter is an error message.
#: backends/eds/lib/edsf-persona-store.vala:876
#: backends/eds/lib/edsf-persona-store.vala:906
#, c-format
msgid "Couldn’t get address book capabilities: %s"
msgstr "ບໍ່ສາມາດຮັບເອົາຄວາມສາມາດຂອງປຶ້ມທີ່ຢູ່ໄດ້: %s"

#. Translators: the parameter is an address book URI.
#: backends/eds/lib/edsf-persona-store.vala:922
#, c-format
msgid "Couldn’t get view for address book ‘%s’."
msgstr "ບໍ່ສາມາດສະແດງຜົນປຶ້ມທີ່ຢູ່ ‘%s’ ໄດ້."

#. Translators: the first parameter is an address book URI
#. * and the second is an error message.
#: backends/eds/lib/edsf-persona-store.vala:1001
#, c-format
msgid "Couldn’t get view for address book ‘%s’: %s"
msgstr "ບໍ່ສາມາດສະແດງຜົນປຶ້ມທີ່ຢູ່ ‘%s’ ໄດ້: %s"

#: backends/eds/lib/edsf-persona-store.vala:1307
msgid "Creating a new contact failed due to reaching the timeout."
msgstr "ການສ້າງລາຍຊື່ຜູ່ຕິດຕໍ່ໃໝ່ລົ້ມເຫຼວເນື່ອງຈາກໝົດເວລາ."

#. Translators: the parameter is the name of a property on a
#. * contact, formatted in the normal GObject style (e.g.
#. * lowercase with hyphens to separate words).
#: backends/eds/lib/edsf-persona-store.vala:1421
#, c-format
msgid "Changing the ‘%s’ property failed due to reaching the timeout."
msgstr "ການປ່ຽນຄຸນສົມບັດ ‘%s’ ລົ້ມເຫຼວເນື່ອງຈາກໝົດເວລາ."

#: backends/eds/lib/edsf-persona-store.vala:1455 folks/avatar-details.vala:63
msgid "Avatar is not writeable on this contact."
msgstr "ຮູບແທນໂຕ (Avatar) ບໍ່ສາມາດແກ້ໄຂໄດ້ໃນລາຍຊື່ຜູ່ຕິດຕໍ່ນີ້."

#: backends/eds/lib/edsf-persona-store.vala:1476
#: folks/web-service-details.vala:123
msgid "Web service addresses are not writeable on this contact."
msgstr "ທີ່ຢູ່ບໍລິການເວັບ (Web service) ບໍ່ສາມາດແກ້ໄຂໄດ້ໃນລາຍຊື່ຜູ່ຕິດຕໍ່ນີ້."

#: backends/eds/lib/edsf-persona-store.vala:1512 folks/url-details.vala:152
msgid "URLs are not writeable on this contact."
msgstr "URL ບໍ່ສາມາດແກ້ໄຂໄດ້ໃນລາຍຊື່ຜູ່ຕິດຕໍ່ນີ້."

#: backends/eds/lib/edsf-persona-store.vala:1594 folks/local-id-details.vala:64
msgid "Local IDs are not writeable on this contact."
msgstr "ID ທ້ອງຖິ່ນບໍ່ສາມາດແກ້ໄຂໄດ້ໃນລາຍຊື່ຜູ່ຕິດຕໍ່ນີ້."

#: backends/eds/lib/edsf-persona-store.vala:1623
msgid "The contact cannot be marked as favourite."
msgstr "ບໍ່ສາມາດໝາຍລາຍຊື່ຜູ່ຕິດຕໍ່ນີ້ເປັນລາຍການທີ່ມັກໄດ້."

#. Translators: the parameter is an error message.
#: backends/eds/lib/edsf-persona-store.vala:1695
#, c-format
msgid "Can’t update avatar: %s"
msgstr "ບໍ່ສາມາດອັບເດດຮູບແທນໂຕ (avatar) ໄດ້: %s"

#: backends/eds/lib/edsf-persona-store.vala:1706 folks/email-details.vala:120
msgid "E-mail addresses are not writeable on this contact."
msgstr "ທີ່ຢູ່ອີເມລບໍ່ສາມາດແກ້ໄຂໄດ້ໃນລາຍຊື່ຜູ່ຕິດຕໍ່ນີ້."

#: backends/eds/lib/edsf-persona-store.vala:1773 folks/phone-details.vala:255
msgid "Phone numbers are not writeable on this contact."
msgstr "ເບີໂທລະສັບບໍ່ສາມາດແກ້ໄຂໄດ້ໃນລາຍຊື່ຜູ່ຕິດຕໍ່ນີ້."

#: backends/eds/lib/edsf-persona-store.vala:1791
#: folks/postal-address-details.vala:362
msgid "Postal addresses are not writeable on this contact."
msgstr "ທີ່ຢູ່ໄປສະນີບໍ່ສາມາດແກ້ໄຂໄດ້ໃນລາຍຊື່ຜູ່ຕິດຕໍ່ນີ້."

#: backends/eds/lib/edsf-persona-store.vala:1862 folks/name-details.vala:454
msgid "Full name is not writeable on this contact."
msgstr "ຊື່ເຕັມບໍ່ສາມາດແກ້ໄຂໄດ້ໃນລາຍຊື່ຜູ່ຕິດຕໍ່ນີ້."

#: backends/eds/lib/edsf-persona-store.vala:1884 folks/name-details.vala:492
msgid "Nickname is not writeable on this contact."
msgstr "ຊື່ຫຼິ້ນບໍ່ສາມາດແກ້ໄຂໄດ້ໃນລາຍຊື່ຜູ່ຕິດຕໍ່ນີ້."

#: backends/eds/lib/edsf-persona-store.vala:1906 folks/note-details.vala:139
msgid "Notes are not writeable on this contact."
msgstr "ບັນທຶກບໍ່ສາມາດແກ້ໄຂໄດ້ໃນລາຍຊື່ຜູ່ຕິດຕໍ່ນີ້."

#: backends/eds/lib/edsf-persona-store.vala:1938 folks/birthday-details.vala:62
